quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  23,75,"Ne kata khubabeelanga tsimbabaasi mana khubarusiliaho obutinyu bwabali ninabo, bakhatsililile mubukori bwabu, nibakoyanile."
  23,76,"Ne toto khwabahelesia eshinyasio (eshilulu) halali shibakalushila Nyasaye wabu Omulesi tawe, ne shibehotselesia tawe."
  23,77,"Okhula shingala khwabekulila omuliango kweshinyasio eshilulu, awo niwo Abandu bawesiakho omwoyo muno."
  23,78,"Ne Ye niye owabalonjela tsimbulililo nende tsindolelo nende emioyo, ne hatiti muno okhupa orio khwenyu."
  23,79,"Naye niye owabaswania khushialo, ne ni ewuwe wamulikhung’asibwa."
  23,80,"Ye niye uhelesinjia obulamu khandi niye ufwisinjia, ne amakalukhano keshilo nende eshitere ni akeke. Koo, shimuparangakhwo tawe?"
  23,81,"Halali baboolanga shingala Abandu bali imbeli baboolanga."
  23,82,"Baboolanga mbu; “Koo, olwa khuliba nikhufwile mana khube liloba nende ebikumba, mbu khokhulilamusibwa?"
  23,83,"Toto khwalakwa kano nende bapapa befu bakhale. Kano ni tsingano tsiakhale butswa.""
  23,84,"Boola mbu; “Liloba nende ebilimwo bioosi ni bia wina toto nikali mbu mumanyile?”"
  23,85,"Balaboola mbu; “Ni bia Nyasaye.” Boola mbu: “Koo, shimwitsulilangakhwo tawe?”"
  23,86,"Boola mbu, "Ni wina Omwami Omulesi wamakulu saba nende Omulesi weshisaala shiobwami eshikhongo?""
  23,87,"Balaboola mbu; “Ni bia Nyasaye.” Boola mbu; “Kho koo, shimuritsanga tawe?”"
  23,88,"Boola mbu; “Ni wina womumukhono kukwe bulimwo obwami bwa buli eshindu, naye niye ulindanga, ne sishilindungwa eshia alenyele tawe, toto nimumanyile (mumbolelekhwo)?""
  23,89,"Balaboola mbu: “Obunyali obo nibwa Nyasaye.” Boola mbu; “Kho mukatibungwa murie?”"